text: Robert Michael Moynihan Jr. (born January 31, 1977) is an American actor, voice actor, comedian and writer. He was on NBC's Saturday Night Live from 2008 to 2017. He also stars as Panda in the 2015 Cartoon Network series We Bare Bears. In August 2016, he married actress Brynn O'Malley. They had their first child in July 2017. ==References== Category:1977 births Category:Living people Category:American television actors Category:Comedians from New York (state)
